      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.deadbeatmillionaireblog.com/?p=85</guid>
      <description>Please Note: This is a blog about the Deadbeat Millionaire.  Click here to visit the official Deadbeat Millionaire site. I am offering a bonus if you purchase the Deadbeat Millionaire through a link on my site.  My bonus is a guide about how I rank my sites in the top positions of Google.  I used [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/deadbeat-millionaire/Deadbeat_Millionaire-Deadbeat_Millionaire_Overview.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><p>Please Note: This is a blog about the <strong>Deadbeat Millionaire</strong>.  <strong><a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.deadbeatmillionaireblog.com/dbmb">Click here to visit the official Deadbeat Millionaire site</a></strong>.</p>
<p>I am offering a bonus if you purchase the Deadbeat Millionaire through a link on my site.  My bonus is a guide about how I rank my sites in the top positions of Google.  I used these techniques to rank this site in position 1 of Google. <a title="Deadbeat Millionaire Bonus" href="http://www.deadbeatmillionaireblog.com/deadbeat-millionaire-bonus/">Click here to find out more about my Deadbeat Millionaire Bonus</a>.</p>
<p><a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.deadbeatmillionaireblog.com/dbmb"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-110" title="Deadbeat millionaire" src="http://www.deadbeatmillionaireblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/Deadbeat-millionaire.png" alt="Deadbeat millionaire Deadbeat Millionaire Overview" width="319" height="108" /></a></p>
<p>The <strong>Deadbeat Millionaire</strong> software is a new product from well-respected and successful internet marketer Dan Brock. This fantastic software automates the process of setting up high converting sites and getting buying traffic to those sites.</p>
<p>Dan’s first product in the Deadbeat Millionaire series was the Deadbeat Super Affiliate, which was a huge success, and it received high praise from customers. The Deadbeat Super Affiliate is a course about selling physical products on the internet using services like Amazon and other Brand Affiliate networks.  The <a title="Deadbeat Millionaire" rel="nofollow" href="http://www.deadbeatmillionaireblog.com/dbmb">Deadbeat Millionaire</a> takes this to the next level.</p>
<p>Dan&#8217;s software works with any affiliate program so you can use it for selling both physical and digital products or even your own products. I really like the fact that you can use it with physical products because there are huge advantages to selling physical products. Although, many Affiliate Marketers will tell you that the money lies in digital products, like those sold on Clickbank, physical products are often far less competitive which makes it easier to enter the market and therefore in many cases a far more viable option.  I personally make the majority of my money through selling physical products.</p>
<h2><strong>Benefits of The Deadbeat Millionaire</strong></h2>
<p>One aspect of the program that I am really excited about is that Dan shows you his own personal successful websites.  One of the greatest ways to be successful is to copy people who are successful.  So imagine having access to affiliate websites that make Dan money on a daily basis and being able to dissect how he created these websites.</p>
<p>Dan also picks niches and shows you how he would go about promoting them. He covers the keywords to use, where to get traffic and where to find backlinks.  He even provides articles based around those niches.</p>
<p>An additional feature of the <em>Deadbeat Millionaire</em> is that every month Dan provides information on possible niches to enter.  This means you can stay up to date with the current trends.</p>
<p>The <em>Deadbeat Millionaire</em> is a feature-packed software.  <a title="Deadbeat Millionaire" rel="nofollow" href="http://www.deadbeatmillionaireblog.com/dbmb"><strong>Click here to find out more about this extraordinary product</strong></a><strong>.</strong></p>
]]></content:encoded>
