      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.deadbeatmillionaireblog.com/?p=44</guid>
      <description>Please Note: This is a blog about the Deadbeat Millionaire. Click here to visit the official Deadbeat Millionaire site. The Deadbeat Millionaire is the latest product to be released by Dan Brock whose other products include Profitzon and The Deadbeat Super Affiliate.  The Deadbeat Super Affiliate received rave reviews from customers so I am really looking [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/deadbeat-millionaire/Deadbeat_Millionaire-What_is_The_Deadbeat_Millionaire.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><p>Please Note: This is a blog about the <strong>Deadbeat Millionaire</strong>. <a title="Deadbeat Millionaire" href="http://www.deadbeatmillionaireblog.com/dbmb"> </a><strong><a title="Deadbeat Millionaire" rel="nofollow" href="http://www.deadbeatmillionaireblog.com/dbmb">Click here to visit the official Deadbeat Millionaire site</a></strong>.</p>
<p><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-52" title="Deadbeat Millionaire" src="http://www.deadbeatmillionaireblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/lazyman-300x274.jpg" alt="lazyman 300x274 What is The Deadbeat Millionaire?" width="300" height="274" /></p>
<p><strong>The Deadbeat Millionaire</strong> is the latest product to be released by Dan Brock whose other products include Profitzon and The Deadbeat Super Affiliate.  The Deadbeat Super Affiliate received rave reviews from customers so I am really looking forward to seeing his latest product.</p>
<p>Now not much information has been released about the <a title="Deadbeat Millionaire" href="http://www.deadbeatmillionaireblog.com/dbmb">Deadbeat Millionaire</a> but it is going to be a software program and from what I understand it will be an accompaniment to the Deadbeat Super Affiliate by automating the processes to an extent. The Deadbeat Super Affiliate is a course based on Dan&#8217;s experience on how to be a successful affiliate with amazon and other brand networks.</p>
<h2>Why am I interested in The Deadbeat MIllionaire?</h2>
<p>The reason I like the idea of this product is because I have had most of my affiliate success on Amazon.  I prefer selling physical products instead of digital ones as they are usually easier to sell.  In addition amazon also has a fantastic reputation so conversions are usually higher than with other merchants and customers are cookied for 24 hours so if they buy anything within  24 hours after they have clicked through to amazon from your link you get a commission for it even if they do not buy the specific product you were advertising. In many cases they buy the product you were advertising and more products as well so you also get a commission for the additional products. The one major downfall with Amazon is that the commissions are quite low so either you have to sell high ticket items or large quantities of low cost items to make it viable.</p>
<p>I must admit that if i did not see the reviews The Deadbeat Super Affiliate received I would not be putting the blog together about <em>The Deadbeat Millionaire</em>.  The reason is I do not really like the branding of the deadbeat product.  It is made to seem that it is easy to make money on the internet and I can tell you from first hand experience it is HARD work.  Don&#8217;t get me wrong I have loved/love every minute of  it though:)</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.deadbeatmillionaireblog.com/dbmb"><span style="font-family: Georgia; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">==&gt;Click Here To Find Out More About The New Deadbeat Millionaire Software&lt;===</span></span></a></strong></p>
]]></content:encoded>
