      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><p><a href="http://www.deadbeatmillionaireblog.com/dbmb" rel="nofollow"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-24" title="Dan Brock" src="http://www.deadbeatmillionaireblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/dan-brock.jpg" alt="dan brock The Deadbeat Millionaire By Dan Brock" width="88" height="78" /></a><strong>The Deadbeat Millionaire</strong> is the next program in the Deadbeat series from well known Internet Marketer Daniel Brock. Dan Brock is also known as &#8220;Dan The Internet Man&#8221; and has been working on the internet for many years.</p>
<p>Currently there are very few details released about the new program, <a title="Deadbeat Millionaire" href="http://www.deadbeatmillionaireblog.com/dbmb" rel="nofollow">The Deadbeat Millionaire</a>, but Dan&#8217;s other Deadbeat program the Deadbeat Super Affiliate was a huge success.  The Deadbeat Super Affiliate is a detailed program on how to sell physical products as an Affiliate with Amazon and other networks. The program is developed from Dan&#8217;s experiences and the personal success that he has achieved as an affiliate.</p>
<p>Based on the previous products released by Dan and his experience as an internet marketer I am looking forward to the release of his new product. I will  be putting together a <em>Deadbeat Millionaire Bonus</em> package for the readers of this blog that purchase the product through my link.</p>
<p>Be sure to bookmark this page so you can find it again when the product is launched.  I will be adding more information to this blog about the upcoming release of the Deadbeat Millionaire as it becomes available so make sure you check back regularly.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
